What is Product Management and and Product Managers responsibilities-

1) Product management requires knowledge of many inter related jobs and processes(strategy, prioritisation, execution, product vision, 
  target customers, value to the customer, advantage over competitors)

1) Product Managers main work is making customer happy

2) Success is measured

Product Manager is the conductor in an orchestra.

PM good to have knowledge of Top-down design and Bottom-up implementation.

====================

Product Triangle - 
Product is the intersection of design, development, and marketing.

